</ol>
</p>
</s:content>
</s:slide>

<s:slide id="asf" status="ready">
<s:title>Apache Software Foundation</s:title>
<s:content>
<p>
<ol>
  <li>1995: To develop a HTTP server</li>
  <li>1999: Incorporated as 501(c)(3) (non-profit)</li>
  <li>Provide a foundation for open collaborative software development</li>
  <li>Provide a legal entity</li>
  <li>Provide a shelter from legal suits</li>
  <li>Protect the Apache brand</li>
</ol>
</p>
</s:content>
</s:slide>

